data.description: Nice 3 bedroom 2 full and 1/2 bath over 1500 sqft in one of Oak Parks nicer low traffic areas offers. Large living room with hardwood floors. Formal dinning room has hardwood floors. Family room off dinning room. Large kitchen with kitchen nook for the kids or family to enjoy a sit down meal. Huge back porch off kitchen prefect for entertaining or ready for the BBQ grill. Master bedroom with full bath. Finished basement with 1/2 bath. Newer windows and roof. Home has central air and hard to find 1 car brick gorge.
